  "en": {
    "description": "I graduated from Marmara University Faculty of Dentistry in 2010, which I entered in 2004. I worked at Bezmialem Vakıf University Faculty of Dentistry for about 1 year. In November 2011, I was appointed as a research assistant to Izmir Katip Çelebi University Faculty of Dentistry.",
    "content": "<p>During my specialty education, I participated in many scientific studies, congresses, courses and symposiums. I have been involved in many academic and clinical studies. I attended training programs at home and abroad. In November 2017, I defended my doctoral thesis on dental implants and received the title of doctor of science in the field of ORAL AND MAXILLOFACIAL SURGERY. Since this date, I have been working as a Maxillofacial Surgery Specialist in Izmir and Manisa. Dental implant applications fall into my special interest.</p> <h3> Articles published in international refereed journals (SCI, SCI-Exp, ESCI) </h3> <ul> <li> Ulu Murat, Soylu Emrah, Kelebek Seyfi̇, Dikici Serkan , Oflaz Hakan (2018). Comparative study of biomechanical stability of resorbable and titanium fixation systems after sagittal split ramus osteotomy with a novel designed in-vitro testing unit. Journal of Cranio-Maxillofacial Surgery, 46 (2), 299-304., Doi: 10.1016 / j.jcms.2017.11.024. </li> <li> Kara M Isa, Ertas Elif Tarım, Ozen Emrullah, Shooter Meral, Aksoy Selami, Erdogan Muharrem Serif, Kelebek Seyfi (2017). Bite Strip analysis of the effect of fluoxetine and paroxetine on sleep bruxism. Archives of Oral Biology http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.archoralbio.2016.12.013, 2017 </li> <li> Karaman O, Kelebek S, Demirci EA, İbiş F, Ulu M, Ercan UK ( 2017). Synergistic Effect of Cold Plasma Treatment and RGD Peptide Coating on Cell Proliferation over Titanium Surfaces. Tissue Eng Rene Med, DOI 10.1007 / s13770-017-0087-5. </li> <li> Saglam Mehmet, Hatipoglu Mükerrem, Koseoglu Serhat, Esen Haci Hasan, Kelebek Seyfi̇ (2014). Boric acid inhibits alveolar bone loss in rats by affecting RANKL and osteoprotegerin expression. Journal of Periodontal Research, 49 (4), 472-479., Doi: 10.1111 / jre.12126. </li> <li> Huseyin Akcay, Murat Ulu, Kelebek Seyfi, Ibrahim Aladag (2016). Benign Paroxysmal Positional Vertigo Following Sinus Floor Elevation in Patient with Antecedents of Vertigo. Journal of Maxillofacial and Oral Surgery. DOI 10.1007 / s12663-016-0891-9 </li> <li> Kara Muhammed Isa, Saim Yanık, Fatih Sarı, Kelebek Seyfi (2016). Simultaneous Retrieval Of Root Fragment, Sınus Lifting With Particulated Bone Graft And Immediate Dental Implant Insertion. Journal Of Craniofacial Surgery 2016 May; 27 (3): e309-11. doi: 10.1097 / SCS.0000000000002554. </li> <li> Ulu Murat, Kelebek Seyfi̇, Kalabalik Fahretti̇n, Akçay Hüseyi̇n (2018). Correlation between decompression period and initial volume of large cystic lesions of the mandible: a retrospective CBCT study. Cukurova Medical Journal, 43 (Annex 1), 254-261., Doi: 10.17826 / cumj.429891 (Publication No: 4373196) </ul> <h3> Articles published in national refereed journals </h3> <ul> <li> Köseoğlu Serhat, Sağlam Mehmet, Kelebek Seyfi (2015). The Importance of Keratinized Mucosa in the Long Term Success of Implants and Palatinal Rotational Stem Flap Application: Case Report. Atatürk University Journal of the Faculty of Dentistry, 25 (2), 221- 225. (Publication No: 1982455) </li> </ul> <h3> Poster presentations presented at international scientific meetings and published in proceedings </h3> <ul> <li> o Ulu Murat, Kelebek Seyfi̇, Akçay Hüseyi̇n, Özen Emrullah, Özgür with Glasses (2014). Osteonekoz in the Jaws Due to Bisphosphonate: A Case Report. Turkish Oral and Maxillofacial Surgery Association 21st International Scientific Congress (Poster) </li> <li> o Ulu Murat, Etöz Osman Abdurrahman, Demi̇rbaş Ahmet Emi̇n, F Gülfeşan Yildirim Çanakçi, Yildirim Mustafa Deni̇zhan, Kelebek Seyfi̇ (2015). Comparison of the Effects of Room Temperature and Heated Local Anesthetic Solutions in Dental Applications. Turkish Oral and Maxillofacial Surgery Association 2015 Scientific Congress (Poster) </li> <li> oAkçay Hüseyi̇n, Kelebek Seyfi̇, Cicik Muhammet Furkan, Görgülü Harun, Çeti̇n Fati̇h, Ulu Murat (2015). Use of Symphysis Graft in Posterior Mandibular Alveolar Crest Augmentation: Three Cases. Turkish Oral and Maxillofacial Association 2015 Scientific Congress (Poster). </li><li> Kelebek Seyfi̇, Keremcan Kuru, Ulu Murat, Akçay Hüseyi̇n (2015). Peripheral Giant Cell Granuloma: A Case Report. Turkish Oral and Maxillofacial Surgery Association 2015 13th Scientific Symposium (Poster). </li> <li> Keremcan Kuru, Akçay Hüseyi̇n, Cicik Muhammet Furkan, Günhan Fati̇h, Toghrul Ali̇yev, Kelebek Seyfi̇ (2015). Oroantral Fistula Treatment with Autogenous Symphysial Block Graft and Implant Placement: Case Report. Turkish Oral and Maxillofacial Surgery Association 2015 Scientific Congress (Poster). </li> <li> Ulu Murat, Kelebek Seyfi̇, Keremcan Kuru, Akçay Hüseyi̇n, Er Ni̇lay (2015). Neurogenic Mass in the Right Mandibular Region: An Undiagnosed Case. Turkish Oral and Maxillofacial Surgery Association 2015 Scientific Congress (Poster). </li> <li> Kelebek Seyfi̇, Özgür with Glasses, Kalabalik Fahretti̇n, Akçay Hüseyi̇n, Cicik Muhammet Furkan, Kara Muhammed İsa (2015). Localized Peripheral Osteoma of the Mandible: A Case Report. Turkish Oral and Maxillofacial Surgery Association 2015 Scientific Congress (Poster). ). </li> <li> Ulu Murat, Kelebek Seyfi̇, Akçay Hüseyi̇n, Oflaz Hakan, Di̇ki̇ci̇ Serkan (2015). Comparison of Stabilized Plate-Screw Fixation Systems with Biomechanical Test after Sagittal Split Ramus Osteotomy. Biyomut 2015 (Poster). ). </li> <li> Kelebek Seyfi, Sayğılı G, Ünal N, Kuru K, Cıcık MF. (2016). Voluntary Reimplantation Practice: A case report. Turkish Oral and Maxillofacial Surgery Association 23rd International Scientific Congress (Poster). </li> <li> Ulu M, Akçay H, Kelebek Seyfi, Eyewear Ö, Ertaş ET, Kalabalık F. (2016). Relationship between decompression time and initial dental volumetric tomography volume in large lesions of the mandible. 23rd International Scientific Congress of Turkish Oral and Maxillofacial Surgery Association (Poster). </li> <li> Demirci EA, Kelebek Seyfi, Ibis F, Ercan UK, Ulu M, Karaman O (2016). The evaluation of wettability and cell-surface interactions on modified titanium discs with Atmospheric Cold Plasma application and RGD peptide conjugation: In vitro study. Conference: 2016 20th National Biomedical Engineering Meeting (BİYOMUT) DOI: 10.1109 / BIYOMUT.2016.7849398. </li> <li> Kuru Keremcan, Efeoğlu Bayram Fatih, Ünal Nuri, Kelebek Seyfi̇, Ulu Murat (2017). Use Of Ring- Bone Technique For Alveolar Defect Repair. 11th International Congress Of The Oral And Maxillofacial Surgery Society. </li> </ul><h3> Oral presentations presented at international scientific meetings and published in proceedings </h3> <ul> <li> Akçay Hüseyi̇n, Ulu Murat, Kelebek Seyfi̇, Cicik Muhammet Furkan (2015). Benign Paroxysmal Positional Vertigo Following Sinus Floor Elevation In Patient With Antecedents Of Vertigo. Turkish Oral and Maxillofacial Surgery Association 22nd International Scientific Congress Bodrum 2015 (Oral Presentation) </li> <li> Ulu Murat, Kütük Nükhet, Cicik Muhammet Furkan, Bi̇lge Süheyb, Kelebek Seyfi̇, Sayğili Suna, Tuğlu Mehmet İbrahi̇m, Alkan Alper ( 2015). Investigation of the Effect of Boric Acid Use on New Bone Formation in Maxillary Sinus Base Elevation. Turkish Oral and Maxillofacial Surgery Association 22nd International Scientific Congress Bodrum 2015 (Oral presentation). </li> <li> Kara Mİ, Erdoğan MŞ, Darıcı A, Özen E, Kelebek Seyfi. (2016) Effects of Boron and Dental Pulp-Originating Mesenchymal Stem Cell Combination on New Bone Formation in Rapid Maxillary Expansion Procedure: Oral presentation. Turkish Oral and Maxillofacial Surgery Association 23rd International Scientific Congress </li> <li> Cicik Muhammet Furkan, Akçay Hüseyi̇n, Ulu Murat, Kelebek Seyfi̇, Bahçeci̇ Selen (2018). Radiographic Investigation of the Effects of Boron and Low Dose Laser Applications on New Bone Tissue Formation in Dissection Osteogenesis. TDB 2nd International Congress of Dentistry </li><li></ul> <h3> IAOMS- ACBID JOINT CONGRESS 2018- 12th Congress. 9-13 May 2018, ANTALYA. </h3> <ul> <li> 24. İzmir Chamber of Dentists International Scientific Congress and Exhibition, 10-12 November 2017, İZMİR. </li> <li> Soft Tissue Arrangements around the Implant in the Aesthetic Region - Individual Abutments and Implant-on-Implant Production Techniques in the Aesthetic Region, Ege University Faculty of Dentistry Seminars , 2016, İZMİR. </li> <li> 25. European Assocciation OF Osseintegration Congress, 29 September- 1 October 2016, PARİS, FRANCE </li> <li> Oral and Maxillofacial Surgery Association Association 1st Assistant School, 5-6 November 2016, ANKARA. </li> <li> Turkish Oral and Maxillofacial Surgery Association 23rd International Scientific Congress, 26-30 May 2016, BODRUM. </li> <li> Central Sterilization Unit Training Program, İzmir Katip Çelebi University Faculty of Dentistry, 7-8 April 2016, İZMİR. </li> <li> Laser Doppler Perfusion Imaging, Laser Doppler Perfusion Monitoring tcpO2 Measurement Training Course, 18-19 February 2016, STOCKHOLM, SWEDEN. </li> <li> 19. Biomedical Engineering National Meeting, 5-6 November 2015, ISTANBUL </li> <li> Turkish Oral and Maxillofacial Surgery Association 13th Scientific Symposium, 23-26 October 2015, TRABZON. </li> <li> Turkish Oral and Maxillofacial Surgery Association 22nd International Scientific Congress, 19-22 May 2015, BODRUM. </li> <li> Turkish Oral and Maxillofacial Surgery Association 21st International Scientific Congress, 18-22 May 2014, BODRUM. </li> <li> Certificate of Use of Experimental Animals, Bezmialem Vakıf University, 10-19 December 2011, İSTANBUL. </li> </ul>",
